strings: <se_def>*: Promote your company! The Black Relic has arrived! You don't know how dangerous the situation here is!
<se_def>*: If so, are you brave or foolish! At that moment, the hero's heart froze!
<se_def>*: Wait... You're not the servant of Dormago, are you?
<se_def>*: Hello! Time to Wait! One cannot strike with the sword and ask such questions in public.
<se_def>*: However, he killed the boss, in short, Tomahi acted alone.
<se_def>*: I'm afraid these people won't accept it. Even if they are “criminal”! beside
<se_high>*: You're right, we're taking a break.
<se_high>*: If they worked for him, I doubt they'd be as brazen as to stroll up here like this.<page>*: No, they'd join him in the ruins via a sinister underground cave...or something...
<se_def>*: Well... I think you're right. Then you'd better throw that sword away.
